{"tid":785578,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一出世係窮L，你一世好有可能都係窮L","createTime":"2018-08-19T10:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T14:13:33.000Z","uid":78827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a4df2d2462cb90c812b37dca9880b169375b3503","tid":785578,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:23:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mVbrgBjZm60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmVbrgBjZm60&d=xQ9dSepvmkXJdIl2SX%2B4mosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=e89b3617\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mVbrgBjZm60</a><br />\n<br />\n睇左條片，講人既自律行為。<br />\n<br />\n出身窮既人，會比較傾向選擇即時享樂高於延遲但更大既享樂。呢樣特質直接降低左出身窮既人長大後成功既機會。<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法可以後天再訓練返果個自律能力出黎？運動訓練？興趣？工作？<br />\n<br />\n我諗係要一步一步，引發小型既自律行為，給予獎賞，再鼓勵更大既自律行為，再俾更大既獎勵，一步一步咁做，就有機會可以訓練到自律能力。<br />\n<br />\n但具體點做，做咩行為，點獎勵，仲未諗到。<br />\n各位巴絲有冇咩諗法？"},{"pid":"522366f2c7f858adedb64a4c57f66eb2e4163d6c","tid":785578,"uid":150881,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"我住私樓但都會及時行樂"},{"pid":"9b94c429269968ed837e919f282944d21c49bf27","tid":785578,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"522366f2c7f858adedb64a4c57f66eb2e4163d6c","tid":785578,"uid":150881,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"我住私樓但都會及時行樂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"及時行樂都有分理唔理性，盲目delay享樂當然唔理性。"},{"pid":"9538b60bd068029dc7e65e1b71cc4508c408b5ec","tid":785578,"uid":114159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"專家發現成功人士的共同特質<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=16218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Farticles%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D16218&d=xQ9dSepvmkXJdIl2SX%2B4mosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=a0d6696a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=16218</a>"},{"pid":"4979e52d62e09e2abe15826296c95c074bdc8bb7","tid":785578,"uid":166434,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"我想架？<br />\n你同我個on9老豆講囉<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"799e74371d5416f391eec7d68793c6c842b054fa","tid":785578,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T11:03:36.000Z","msg":"短視 同 遠見既分别"},{"pid":"746f341820635bcf40fce45c02b796c04d951f10","tid":785578,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"799e74371d5416f391eec7d68793c6c842b054fa","tid":785578,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T11:03:36.000Z","msg":"短視 同 遠見既分别"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:28:51.000Z","msg":"係，但如果只係明知自己短視，而去逼自己做遠見既決定，會積累壓力，唔長久，好快會反彈。"},{"pid":"f786340d26e000e87e59289175c2c50cfbfce2b2","tid":785578,"uid":45582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:30:31.000Z","msg":"其實敗家嘅二世祖都唔少"},{"pid":"c0fd2274fd317a39fd1cb5b499625ded0b57cd76","tid":785578,"uid":167757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:13:33.000Z","msg":"其實自律係啲乜嘢野嚟？<br />\n忍耐力高嗎？<br />\n的而且確，如果我忍耐力高我就唔會及時行樂<br />\n<br />\n但如果我係一個情緒化的人又會點樣<br />\n係我在意或者情緒失控時我的自律性就會下降，但我平時又會好有自律性，咁我算唔算自律性高？<br />\n<br />\n好多時自律性高與低我覺得好睇原生家庭父母榜樣。靠後天的話就理大家都識講但到做的時候又係另一回事，及時行樂"}]}